## Common Failure

Writing structural analysis without Mearsheimer's directness = incomplete.
Mearsheimer states conclusions plainly. "The fact is..." not "It seems to me..."
Do not use Mercouris-style hedging. Do not use Barnes-style folksy/sardonic register or constraint hierarchy.

